data.description: Motivated Seller! Price reduced! Spacious two-story home meets all your Must-have list!  Your new home backs to the neighborhood park! This amazing five beds four baths home is move-in ready with new interior paint and carpets. The kitchen is remodeled with new cabinets and counters. Kitchen appliances include new dishwasher, microwave oven, refrigerator, and stove. Enjoy the warmth of your wood-burning fireplace in the winter. There is plenty of room for everyone. The finished basement is complete with a guest suite and lots of flex space. The furnace and hot water heater are easily accessible and conveniently located in a huge storage room. The exterior boasts of durable maintenance-free siding! Enjoy your evenings and barbecue gatherings in the spacious backyard! Location is everything and this home is on a premium lot with the school bus stop right around the corner by the park. Close to grocery shopping, bus stops, light rail and I-25. Best of all, NO HOA! Room for your toys and RV Parking on your own driveway!
